                                    Platform Event
                                ----------------------

  Platform Event: - It is the features of streaming api which work on event driven architecture like publish and subscriber model.

    Notes:-  once we publish the event,event producer will publish it will go to the event bus. event consumer will consume the 
             services only when the consumer has subscribed the event.

    Process of creating Platform event in salesforce : - setup --> search Platform event and click--> New Platform event -->create.

    Publish behavior: - while creating Platform event there is option publish immediately or publish after commit.
                        a). publish immediately : - Platform event will be published when publish call executed it does not care whether record success or failed.
                        b). publish after commit: - It will publish event when transaction commited successfully to the database. like order confirmed.

   After platform event created: - Api name like: -Order_Detail__e should be suffix with __e.
  
   once Platform event got created by default 4 standard field got created as well.
                  1). CreatedBy : - store the created by whom
                  2). CreatedDate: - store the createddate
                  3). ReplayId: - It will be populated by the system when publish executed and reached to the event bus.a subcriber can store the replay id value and use it for resubcription purpose. As event bus hold for 3days.and replay id is sequential number like 121, 122 ......
                  4). EventUuid: - 

      we can create the custom fields to hold the temporay data. but 6 data types only support like text,textarea, number,
              data, datetime and checkbox.


                                                          
            
